    "5 and 6 demonstrates that the model's predictions are unstable if text with many different classes is used.",
    "By comparing Figs.",
    "7 and 8, it can be seen that the model has problems distinguishing between background and outcome.",
    "A possible explanation is that background and outcome often have a similar writing style, which means that it is not possible to differentiate it exactly and it tends to be estimated as outcome.",
